results.title: Remote-based Senior Dynamics AX Developer - GBP375 a day
results.description: Remote-based Senior Dynamics AX Developer - £375 a day An AX2012 end user is currently seeking a contract resource to assist with their AX development. This interim role for on a 3-6 month basis initially with the potential for extension. Skills required: - AX2012 development experience - Fluency with X / Morphx - AX report writing - SSRS This opportunity is with a Leeds based organisation, however remote working is available.
